  "motivation": "Without this change, developers must rely on inconsistent MIME sniffing behavior across browsers, which can lead to incorrect content handling. Aligning with the spec ensures predictable behavior and improves interoperability.\n\nRecent WPT additions (PR 54219) https://github.com/web-platform-tests/wpt/pull/54219",
