  "api_spec": false,
  "automation_spec": false,
  "interop_compat_risks": "Interoperability risk is low.\n\nvery low compat risk; only malformed MIME types with +json in module scripts newly rejected. Other browsers are already stricter. Additionally, until recently (https://groups.google.com/u/0/a/chromium.org/g/blink-dev/c/-lZFLXH7_Y8/m/hw3Tcl64AQAJ), all such +json MIME types would have been treated as failures, making it highly unlikely that there are widespread dependencies on this invalid subset.",
